👉 What does Abstract (class) mean 
Abstract in english means -> existing in thought or as an idea without physical or concrete existance

👉 Abstract Method
A method that is declared without an implementation 
                                            abstract void moveTo(double X , double Y)

👉 Abstract Class
If a class includes abstract methods , then the class itself must be declared abstract , as in :
                                            public abstract class PhoneModel{
                                                abstract void Switchoff();
                                            }
When an abstract class is subclassed , the subclass usually provides implementations for all of the methods
